Symbol.Script_3D:
unID=sh_unID
if gs_opening_dir_m = 1 then eloj_ref = -1 else eloj_ref = 1 endif
if bUseDifferentAngles then opAngleForRotateHorizontal = opAngle_horizontal2 else opAngleForRotateHorizontal = opAngle_horizontal endif ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ! --- Open the Window with Hotspots --- ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
if gs_full_edit then
! --- Side-hung ----------------------------------------------------------------
if gs_optype_m = OPTYPE_SIDEHUNG then addx -a / 2 addy b / 2 rotx -90 addy -gs_sash_thk / 2
if bUseDifferentAngles then hotspot a, -gs_sash_thk/2, 0, unID, opAngle_horizontal2, 4+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, -1*eloj_ref, unID, opAngle_horizontal2, 7 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a*sin(90+opAngle_horizontal2)+gs_sash_thk/2*cos(90+opAngle_horizontal2),a*cos(90+opAngle_horizontal2)-gs_sash_thk/2*sin(90+opAngle_horizontal2),0, unID, opAngle_horizontal2, 5 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, opAngle_horizontal2, 6 : unID=unID+1 else hotspot a, -gs_sash_thk/2, 0, unID, opAngle_horizontal, 4+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, -1*eloj_ref, unID, opAngle_horizontal, 7 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a*sin(90+opAngle_horizontal)+gs_sash_thk/2*cos(90+opAngle_horizontal),a*cos(90+opAngle_horizontal)-gs_sash_thk/2*sin(90+opAngle_horizontal),0, unID, opAngle_horizontal, 5 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, opAngle_horizontal, 6 : unID=unID+1 endif
del 3
if abs (opAngleForRotateHorizontal) > eps then addz gs_rebate_depth roty -opAngleForRotateHorizontal addz -gs_rebate_depth endif
addx a/2 endif
! --- Top-hung -----------------------------------------------------------------
if gs_optype_m = OPTYPE_TOPHUNG then addy b rotz -90 rotx -90 addy -gs_sash_thk/2
hotspot b, -gs_sash_thk/2, 0, unID, opAngle_vertical, 4+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, -1*eloj_ref, unID, opAngle_vertical, 7 : unID=unID+1 hotspot b*sin(90+opAngle_vertical)+gs_sash_thk/2*cos(90+opAngle_vertical),b*cos(90+opAngle_vertical)-gs_sash_thk/2*sin(90+opAngle_vertical),0, unID, opAngle_vertical, 5 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, opAngle_vertical, 6 : unID=unID+1
del 3
if abs (opAngle_vertical) > eps then addz gs_rebate_depth rotx -opAngle_vertical addz -gs_rebate_depth endif
addy -b endif
! --- Side-hung Mirrored -------------------------------------------------------
if gs_optype_m = OPTYPE_SIDEHUNGMIRRORED then !side-hung right mulx -1 addx -a/2 addy b/2 rotx -90 addy -gs_sash_thk/2
if bUseDifferentAngles then hotspot a, -gs_sash_thk/2, 0, unID, opAngle_horizontal2, 4+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, 1*eloj_ref, unID, opAngle_horizontal2, 7 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a*sin(90+opAngle_horizontal2)+gs_sash_thk/2*cos(90+opAngle_horizontal2),a*cos(90+opAngle_horizontal2)-gs_sash_thk/2*sin(90+opAngle_horizontal2),0, unID, opAngle_horizontal2, 5 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, opAngle_horizontal2, 6 : unID=unID+1 else hotspot a, -gs_sash_thk/2, 0, unID, opAngle_horizontal, 4+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, 1*eloj_ref, unID, opAngle_horizontal, 7 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a*sin(90+opAngle_horizontal)+gs_sash_thk/2*cos(90+opAngle_horizontal),a*cos(90+opAngle_horizontal)-gs_sash_thk/2*sin(90+opAngle_horizontal),0, unID, opAngle_horizontal, 5 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, opAngle_horizontal, 6 : unID=unID+1 endif
del 3
if abs (opAngleForRotateHorizontal) > eps then addz gs_rebate_depth roty -opAngleForRotateHorizontal addz -gs_rebate_depth endif
addx a/2 mulx -1 endif
! --- Bottom-hung --------------------------------------------------------------
if gs_optype_m = OPTYPE_BOTTOMHUNG then muly -1 rotz -90 rotx -90 addy -gs_sash_thk/2
hotspot b, -gs_sash_thk/2, 0, unID, opAngle_vertical, 4+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, 1*eloj_ref, unID, opAngle_vertical, 7 : unID=unID+1 hotspot b*sin(90+opAngle_vertical)+gs_sash_thk/2*cos(90+opAngle_vertical),b*cos(90+opAngle_vertical)-gs_sash_thk/2*sin(90+opAngle_vertical),0, unID, opAngle_vertical, 5 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, opAngle_vertical, 6 : unID=unID+1
del 3
if abs (opAngle_vertical) > eps then addz gs_rebate_depth rotx -opAngle_vertical addz -gs_rebate_depth endif
muly -1 endif
! --- Reversible ---------------------------------------------------------------
if gs_optype_m = OPTYPE_REVERSIBLE then addy b/2 rotx -90 addy gs_sash_thk/2
hotspot gs_sash_thk*sin(135)+a/2*sin(90), gs_sash_thk*cos(135)+a/2*cos(90), (0), unID, opAngle_horizontal, 4+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot gs_sash_thk*sin(90)+a/2*sin(0), gs_sash_thk*cos(90)+a/2*cos(0), 0, unID, opAngle_horizontal, 7 : unID=unID+1 hotspot gs_sash_thk*sin(180+opAngle_horizontal)+a/2*sin(90+opAngle_horizontal), gs_sash_thk*cos(180+opAngle_horizontal)+a/2*cos(90+opAngle_horizontal), (0), unID, opAngle_horizontal, 5 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, -gs_sash_thk, (0), unID, opAngle_horizontal, 6 : unID=unID+1
del 2
if abs (opAngle_horizontal) > eps then addz gs_rebate_depth roty -opAngle_horizontal addz -gs_rebate_depth endif
addy -b/2 endif
! --- Sliding-left -------------------------------------------------------------
if gs_optype_m = OPTYPE_SLIDINGLEFT then hotspot a/2, b/2, 0, unID, opWidth3d, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 2*a, b/2, 0, unID, opWidth3d, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a/2-opWidth3d, b/2, 0, unID, opWidth3d, 2 : unID=unID+1
if opWidth3d > owlen_a then opWidth3d = owlen_a if opWidth3d < 0 then opWidth3d = 0
addx -opWidth3d endif
! --- Sliding-right ------------------------------------------------------------
if gs_optype_m = OPTYPE_SLIDINGRIGHT then hotspot -a/2, b/2, 0, unID, opWidth3d, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot -a, b/2, 0, unID, opWidth3d, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot -a/2+opWidth3d, b/2, 0, unID, opWidth3d, 2 : unID=unID+1
if opWidth3d > owlen_a then opWidth3d = owlen_a if opWidth3d < 0 then opWidth3d = 0
addx opWidth3d endif
! --- Sliding-up ---------------------------------------------------------------
if gs_optype_m = OPTYPE_SLIDINGUP then hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, opWidth3d, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, -1, 0, unID, opWidth3d, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0+opWidth3d, 0, unID, opWidth3d, 2 : unID=unID+1
if opWidth3d > owlen_a then opWidth3d = owlen_a if opWidth3d < 0 then opWidth3d = 0
addy opWidth3d endif
! --- Sliding-down -------------------------------------------------------------
if gs_optype_m = OPTYPE_SLIDINGDOWN then hotspot 0, b, 0, unID, opWidth3d, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, b+1, 0, unID, opWidth3d, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, b-opWidth3d, 0, unID, opWidth3d, 2 : unID=unID+1
if opWidth3d>owlen_a then opWidth3d=owlen_a if opWidth3d<0 then opWidth3d=0
addy -opWidth3d endif
! --- Tilt-turn ----------------------------------------------------------------
if gs_optype_m = OPTYPE_TILTTURN then addx -a/2 addy b/2 rotx -90 addy -gs_sash_thk/2
hotspot a, -gs_sash_thk/2, 0, unID, opAngle_horizontal, 4+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, -1*eloj_ref, unID, opAngle_horizontal, 7 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a*sin(90+opAngle_horizontal)+gs_sash_thk/2*cos(90+opAngle_horizontal),a*cos(90+opAngle_horizontal)-gs_sash_thk/2*sin(90+opAngle_horizontal),0, unID, opAngle_horizontal, 5 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, opAngle_horizontal, 6 : unID=unID+1
del 4
muly -1 rotz -90 rotx -90 addy -gs_sash_thk/2
hotspot b, -gs_sash_thk/2, 0, unID, opAngle_vertical, 4+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, 1*eloj_ref, unID, opAngle_vertical, 7 : unID=unID+1 hotspot b*sin(90+opAngle_vertical)+gs_sash_thk/2*cos(90+opAngle_vertical),b*cos(90+opAngle_vertical)-gs_sash_thk/2*sin(90+opAngle_vertical),0, unID, opAngle_vertical, 5 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, opAngle_vertical, 6 : unID=unID+1
del 4
if abs(opAngle_vertical) > eps then muly -1
if abs (opAngle_vertical) > eps then addz gs_rebate_depth rotx -opAngle_vertical addz -gs_rebate_depth endif
muly -1 endif
if abs (opAngle_horizontal) > eps then addx -a/2
if abs (opAngle_horizontal) > eps then addz gs_rebate_depth roty -opAngle_horizontal addz -gs_sash_thk/2 endif addx a/2 endif endif
! --- Tilt-turn Mirrored -------------------------------------------------------
if gs_optype_m = OPTYPE_TILTTURNMIRRORED then mulx -1 addx -a/2 addy b/2 rotx -90 addy -gs_sash_thk/2
hotspot a, -gs_sash_thk/2, 0, unID, opAngle_horizontal, 4+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, 1*eloj_ref, unID, opAngle_horizontal, 7 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a*sin(90+opAngle_horizontal)+gs_sash_thk/2*cos(90+opAngle_horizontal),a*cos(90+opAngle_horizontal)-gs_sash_thk/2*sin(90+opAngle_horizontal),0, unID, opAngle_horizontal, 5 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, opAngle_horizontal, 6 : unID=unID+1
del 5
muly -1 rotz -90 rotx -90 addy -gs_sash_thk/2
hotspot b, -gs_sash_thk/2, 0, unID, opAngle_vertical, 4+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, 1*eloj_ref, unID, opAngle_vertical, 7 : unID=unID+1 hotspot b*sin(90+opAngle_vertical)+gs_sash_thk/2*cos(90+opAngle_vertical),b*cos(90+opAngle_vertical)-gs_sash_thk/2*sin(90+opAngle_vertical),0, unID, opAngle_vertical, 5 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, opAngle_vertical, 6 : unID=unID+1
del 4
if abs (opAngle_vertical) > eps then muly -1
if abs (opAngle_vertical) > eps then addz gs_rebate_depth rotx -opAngle_vertical addz -gs_rebate_depth endif
muly -1 endif
if abs (opAngle_horizontal) > eps then mulx -1 addx -a/2
if abs (opAngle_horizontal) > eps then addz gs_rebate_depth roty -opAngle_horizontal addz -gs_rebate_depth endif
addx a/2 mulx -1 endif endif endif
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ! --- Grids --- ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ if gs_frame_mat = gs_frame_mat2 then ! One body, in case of similar materials in_out_cikl = 1 else in_out_cikl = 2 endif
if gs_grill_mat = gs_grill_mat2 then ! One body, in case of similar materials in_out_cikl_gr = 1 else in_out_cikl_gr = 2 endif
if grill_m = 2 then for ijk= 1 to in_out_cikl_gr for i = 1 to nVertPanel_2 if vergrid_2[i][1]<grillWidth_vert_2 then vergrid_2[i][1]=grillWidth_vert_2 if vergrid_2[i][1]>a-2*gs_sash_width+2*fix_sh_grmod then vergrid_2[i][1]=a-2*gs_sash_width+2*fix_sh_grmod
if vergrid_2[i][3]>b-gs_sash_width+fix_sh_grmod then vergrid_2[i][3]=b-gs_sash_width+fix_sh_grmod if vergrid_2[i][2]<=gs_sash_width-fix_sh_grmod then vergrid_2[i][2]=gs_sash_width-fix_sh_grmod
if vergrid_2[i][2]>b-gs_sash_width+fix_sh_grmod then vergrid_2[i][2]=b-gs_sash_widt+fix_sh_grmod if vergrid_2[i][3]<=gs_sash_width-fix_sh_grmod then vergrid_2[i][3]=gs_sash_width-fix_sh_grmod next i
for i = 1 to nHorPanel_2 if horgrid_2[i][1]<grillWidth_hor_2 then horgrid_2[i][1]=grillWidth_hor_2 if horgrid_2[i][1]>b-2*gs_sash_width+2*fix_sh_grmod then horgrid_2[i][1]=b-2*gs_sash_width+2*fix_sh_grmod
if horgrid_2[i][3]>a-gs_sash_width+fix_sh_grmod then horgrid_2[i][3]=a-gs_sash_width+fix_sh_grmod if horgrid_2[i][2]<=gs_sash_width-fix_sh_grmod then horgrid_2[i][2]=gs_sash_width-fix_sh_grmod
if horgrid_2[i][2]>a-gs_sash_width+fix_sh_grmod then horgrid_2[i][2]=a-gs_sash_width+fix_sh_grmod if horgrid_2[i][3]<=gs_sash_width-fix_sh_grmod then horgrid_2[i][3]=gs_sash_width-fix_sh_grmod next i
if nVertPanel_2>=1 then if gs_full_edit then add (-a/2+gs_sash_width-grillWidth_vert_2/2-fix_sh_grmod), 0, gz-fix_sh_grshift for i=1 to nVertPanel_2 lenghtv=vergrid_2[i][2]+(vergrid_2[i][3]-vergrid_2[i][2])/2
hotspot 0, lenghtv, 0, unID, vergrid_2[i][1], 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot -1, lenghtv, 0, unID, vergrid_2[i][1], 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot vergrid_2[i][1], lenghtv, 0, unID, vergrid_2[i][1], 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot vergrid_2[i][1], 0, 0, unID, vergrid_2[i][2], 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot vergrid_2[i][1], -1, 0, unID, vergrid_2[i][2], 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot vergrid_2[i][1], vergrid_2[i][2]+grillWidth_vert_2/2, 0, unID, vergrid_2[i][2], 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot vergrid_2[i][1], 0, 0, unID, vergrid_2[i][3], 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot vergrid_2[i][1], -1, 0, unID, vergrid_2[i][3], 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot vergrid_2[i][1], vergrid_2[i][3]-grillWidth_vert_2/2, 0, unID, vergrid_2[i][3], 2 : unID=unID+1
next i del 1 endif endif
! --- Horizontal grids ---
if nHorPanel_2 > 0 then if gs_full_edit then add -a/2 , -grillWidth_hor_2/2+gs_sash_width-fix_sh_grmod, gz-fix_sh_grshift for i=1 to nHorPanel_2 lenghth=horgrid_2[i][2]+(horgrid_2[i][3]-horgrid_2[i][2])/2
hotspot lenghth, 0, 0, unID, horgrid_2[i][1], 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot lenghth, -1, 0, unID, horgrid_2[i][1], 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot lenghth, horgrid_2[i][1], 0, unID, horgrid_2[i][1], 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot 0, horgrid_2[i][1], 0, unID, horgrid_2[i][2], 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot -1, horgrid_2[i][1], 0, unID, horgrid_2[i][2], 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot horgrid_2[i][2]+grillWidth_hor_2/2, horgrid_2[i][1], 0, unID, horgrid_2[i][2], 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot 0, horgrid_2[i][1], 0, unID, horgrid_2[i][3], 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot -1, horgrid_2[i][1], 0, unID, horgrid_2[i][3], 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot horgrid_2[i][3]-grillWidth_hor_2/2, horgrid_2[i][1], 0, unID, horgrid_2[i][3], 2 : unID=unID+1 next i del 1 endif endif
addz part_thk_grill
part_thk_grill = gth - out_thk_grill next ijk del in_out_cikl_gr endif
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ! --- Calling sash --- ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
call "sash" parameters a = a, b = b,
! --- Options ------------------------------------------ gs_opening_dir_m = gs_opening_dir_m, gs_optype_m = gs_optype_m, opWidth3d = opWidth3d, gs_SashText_typ_num = gs_SashText_typ_num,
! --- Frame -------------------------------------------- gs_frame_width = gs_frame_width, gs_frame_thk = gs_frame_thk, gs_rebate_width = gs_rebate_width,
! --- Sash --------------------------------------------- grill_m = grill_m, gs_sash_thk = gs_sash_thk, gs_sash_width = gs_sash_width, gs_glass_thk = gs_glass_thk, nHorPanel = nHorPanel_2, nVertPanel = nVertPanel_2, grillPosition_m = grillPosition_m, gth = gth, grillWidth_hor = grillWidth_hor_2, grillWidth_vert = grillWidth_vert_2, horgrid = horgrid_2, vergrid = vergrid_2, glassFromLeft = glassFromLeft, glassFromRight = glassFromRight, glassFromTop = glassFromTop, glassFromBottom = glassFromBottom, gs_cust_panel = gs_cust_panel, gs_handle_typ_m = gs_handle_typ_m, gs_han_pos = gs_han_pos, gs_han_height = gs_han_height, gs_cust_handle = gs_cust_handle, flipHandle = flipHandle,
! --- 2D Rep ------------------------------------------- gs_frame_pen_cont = gs_frame_pen_cont, gs_fillSash = gs_fillSash, gs_penSash_fg = gs_penSash_fg, gs_penSash_bg = gs_penSash_bg,
! --- 3D Rep ------------------------------------------- gs_detlevel_3d_m = gs_detlevel_3d_m, gs_shadow = gs_shadow, gs_resol = gs_resol, gs_frame_pen = gs_frame_pen, gs_glass_pen = gs_glass_pen,
! --- Materials ---------------------------------------- gs_frame_mat = gs_frame_mat, gs_frame_mat2 = gs_frame_mat2, gs_glass_mat = gs_glass_mat, gs_grill_mat = gs_grill_mat, gs_grill_mat2 = gs_grill_mat2, matHandle = matHandle, matHandleAcc = matHandleAcc,
! --- Others ------------------------------------------- isWindow = isWindow, ! --- MVO Override ------------------------------------------- or_bOplines3d = or_bOplines3d, or_iOpLineType3dIn = or_iOpLineType3dIn, or_iOpLineType3dOut = or_iOpLineType3dOut, or_iOplineStyle = or_iOplineStyle, or_opLinePen = or_opLinePen, bOverride_MVO_3D = bOverride_MVO_3D
end
Symbol.Script_1D:
eps = 0.0001
! opening type OPTYPE_FIX = 1 OPTYPE_SIDEHUNG = 2 OPTYPE_SIDEHUNGMIRRORED = 3 OPTYPE_BOTTOMHUNG = 4 OPTYPE_TOPHUNG = 5 OPTYPE_TILTTURN = 6 OPTYPE_TILTTURNMIRRORED = 7 OPTYPE_REVERSIBLE = 8 OPTYPE_SLIDINGLEFT = 11 OPTYPE_SLIDINGRIGHT = 12 OPTYPE_SLIDINGUP = 13 OPTYPE_SLIDINGDOWN = 14
v1 = 0.08 !*** 1 dash length v2 = 0.05 !*** 1 space length
nHorPanel_2 = nHorPanel_2 - 1 ! : Grids=>Panels nVertPanel_2 = nVertPanel_2 - 1
if nVertPanel_2 < 0 then nVertPanel_2 = 0 if nHorPanel_2 < 0 then nHorPanel_2 = 0
if gs_optype_m = OPTYPE_FIX then fix_sh_grmod = gs_sash_width-gs_frame_width/2 fix_sh_grshift = gs_frame_thk/2 else fix_sh_grmod = 0 fix_sh_grshift = 0 endif
if gs_optype_m = OPTYPE_REVERSIBLE then a = a - 2*gs_rebate_width b = b - 2*gs_rebate_width endif
hgnn=((a-2*gs_sash_width+grillWidth_vert_2+2*fix_sh_grmod)/(nVertPanel_2+1))-grillWidth_vert_2
! Sliding windows opening
if opWidth3d>owlen_a then opWidth3d=owlen_a parameters opWidth3d=owlen_a endif
if opWidth3d<0 then opWidth3d=0 parameters opWidth3d=0 endif
! --- Grill position ---
if grillPosition_m = 1 then gz=gs_sash_thk/2-gs_glass_thk/2-gth
if grillPosition_m = 2 then gz=gs_sash_thk/2+gs_glass_thk/2
if grillPosition_m = 3 then gz=gs_sash_thk/2-gth/2

Boolean.Name: bUseDifferentAngles
Boolean.Description: "Use Opening Angle 2 instead of Opening Angle"
